error.msg: Boolean result is used in bitwise operation. Clarify expression with parentheses.
error.verbose: Suspicious expression. Boolean result is used in bitwise operation. The operator '!' and the comparison operators have higher precedence than bitwise operators. It is recommended that the expression is clarified with parentheses.

error.msg: Variable 'm_items' is assigned in constructor body. Consider performing initialization in initialization list.
error.verbose: When an object of a class is created, the constructors of all member variables are called consecutively in the order the variables are declared, even if you don't explicitly write them to the initialization list. You could avoid assigning 'm_items' a value by passing the value to the constructor in the initialization list.
